    "biography": "<p>Elementals are incarnations of the elements that compose existence.</p><p>A fire elemental cannot enter water or any other nonflammable liquid. A body of water is an impassible barrier unless the fire elemental can step or jump over it.</p><p>Fire elementals speak Ignan, though they rarely choose to do so.</p><p>A fire elemental is a fierce opponent that attacks its enemies directly and savagely. It takes joy in burning the creatures and objects of the Material Plane to ashes.</p>",
